				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=1162">Neriak</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>Lokar ToBiath</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Lokar ToBiath</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=16810"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:gordon@climax.co.uk">Enki Ravensoul</a> | 
		                        12/18/1999 5:19:15 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">If you give a red wine to Lokar ToBiath in the wizard's guild in 3rd gate, he starts gibbering about a scribe of Teir'Dal.<BR>
(faction up with dread guards and dark bargainers)<BR>
<BR>
You then have to bribe him with 70 gold coins to reveal the location of this scribe, he also gives you a note to give to her.<BR>
(again, faction up with dread guards and dark bargainers)<BR>
<BR>
The scribe is the barmaid downstairs in the blind fish, give the note to her.<BR>
(faction up with dread guards and dark bargainers)<BR>
She gives you a note back saying she wants Lokar ToBiath's head,<BR>
<BR>
Now this is where I've stopped, I don't know what faction hits I'll get for killing ToBiath and I don't particularly want to end up KOS in my own home city.<BR>
<BR>
If you complete her request, she apparently gives you the book of turmoil, which is part of a larger quest given by the oracle in the ocean of tears (if you give him the book he gives you a glowing torch, ac7 +5 cha, which you can get off an NPC name Trelise(sp?) in Lavastorm anyway).<BR>
<BR>
Can anyone tell me how much of a faction hit I'll get for killing ToBiath ?
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
