				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Thanks to everyone for all the other info. On this quest. Now here's so more. <BR>
<BR>
Lokar is quite easy after a while, I killed him easily at 12 and easier now that I am 20.  You should have fun killing him since at this high of a level I resisted all of his spells. Also take note Lokar has a pet a measly lvl 4 skele I think.  The only problem is for Lokar who stands so close to the wall in hi spawn place the pet he casts summons out side the building so it can't help him.  The thing often wanders around 3rd gate and I have seen hanging out in the Necro guild.  Once it attacked me and was rather pitiful because by the time it ran across town to get me I already killed its master:)  Anyways, his faction drop does not do much, I have killed him for time without doing his quest and our guards and merchants still apparently don't care.<BR>
<BR>
It used to say your faction with traitors goes down as well.  I only saw this once before when I killed the Necro heretic in Lava Storm that spawns at the goblin camp.<BR>
<BR>
Have fun killing Lokar!!!!<BR>
